      • IS_SMELL_CHECKING_ENABLED

        public static final boolean IS_SMELL_CHECKING_ENABLED
        Boolean value to indicate whether an exception should be thrown for smells. A smell is something that looks wrong, but there is a possibility that it is correct.

        This should be disabled before a production build is launched.

        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • IS_SLOW_ACCESS_ENABLED

        public static final boolean IS_SLOW_ACCESS_ENABLED
        Boolean value to indicate whether intensive accesses should be slowed. The primary purpose is to make it easier to test asynchronous operations in the UI.

        This is a development feature only and MUST be disabled in production builds of the app.

        See Also:
        SLOW_ACCESS_DELAY_MILLISECONDS, Constant Field Values
